#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/main.qml:1156
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/main.qml:1194
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/main.qml:1197
